{"tid":1773114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國發表報告 指以色列長期非法佔領 造成巴勒斯坦經濟年損25億美元","createTime":"2019-12-07T08:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T13:12:49.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd1d2d4712cd29ac16e9351571c7b13d017bd92","tid":1773114,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:18:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/un-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258B%2592%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259D%25A6%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2590%258D25%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583-145530536.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2Fun-%2525E4%2525BB%2525A5%2525E8%252589%2525B2%2525E5%252588%252597%2525E9%252595%2525B7%2525E6%25259C%25259F%2525E4%2525BD%252594%2525E9%2525A0%252598-%2525E9%252580%2525A0%2525E6%252588%252590%2525E5%2525B7%2525B4%2525E5%25258B%252592%2525E6%252596%2525AF%2525E5%25259D%2525A6%2525E7%2525B6%252593%2525E6%2525BF%25259F%2525E5%2525B9%2525B4%2525E6%252590%25258D25%2525E5%252584%252584%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E5%252585%252583-145530536.html&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=efb4cece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/un-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258B%2592%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259D%25A6%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2590%258D25%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583-145530536.html</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國報告指出，以色列長期佔領巴勒斯坦領土，造成巴勒斯坦人在過去20年間，每年的經濟損失超過25億美元。圖為今年7月以色列部隊強拆巴勒斯坦民宅，引發國際關切。(資料照片／AFP)<br />\n聯合國今天(2日)公布的一份報告指出，以色列長期佔領巴勒斯坦領土，造成巴勒斯坦人在過去20年間，每年的經濟損失超過25億美元。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國貿易和發展會議(UN Conference on Trade and Development, UNCTAD)今天公布的報告，估計巴勒斯坦政府在2000年到2017年間，整體財政損失多達477億美元。<br />\n<br />\n這項數字包括280億美元的應計利息(accrued interest)和巴勒斯坦財政收入流失的66億美元。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國的這份報告指出，巴勒斯坦將近20年的經濟損失金額，足夠削減巴勒斯坦政府在同一段期間內產生的177億美元預算赤字。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國的報告指出，若是過去18年間，巴勒斯坦損失的477億美元，妥善投資於貧瘠的巴勒斯坦經濟，可望創造出200萬個就業機會，或是每年11萬個就業機會。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國是在約旦河西岸(West Bank)城市雷馬拉(Ramallah)的「巴勒斯坦經濟政策研究所」(Palestine Economic Policy Research Institute)，對外公布這份報告。<br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦經濟政策研究所的資深研究員賈米爾(Misyef Jameel)說，聯合國的這份報告僅評估以色列的長期佔領，對巴勒斯坦造成的直接財政影響。<br />\n<br />\n然而他表示，巴勒斯坦實際的財政損失比聯合國的估計似乎要高出許多。"},{"pid":"f84f30f43592856a7c975745284d9cef0c23a4b3","tid":1773114,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01236832550ab6784134b45fbe5799d39ecdcb4e","tid":1773114,"uid":89514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50